  "serviceName": "companyAddresses",
  "content": "<p><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Overview:</strong></p><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Company Addresses module maintains the address information associated with companies in the system. It allows Admins to store and manage company location details such as street addresses, city, state, province, country, and postcode.</span></p><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">These address records help maintain proper company information and support organizational and operational management within the application.</span></p><h3><br></h3><h3><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Steps to Manage Company Addresses:</strong></h3><p><br></p><ol><li data-list=\"ordered\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Admin</strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> can navigate to </span><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Company Addresses</strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> from the menu.</span></li><li data-list=\"ordered\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Click the </span><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Add</strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> button to create a new company address and enter details such as: </span><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Company, Street 1, Street 2, Postcode, City, State, Province, Country, Is Default</strong></li><li data-list=\"ordered\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Existing company address records can be </span><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">viewed, edited,</strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> or </span><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">deleted</strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> as needed.</span></li><li data-list=\"ordered\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Admins can use the table features to: Search company addresses using keyword search, Filter records, Hide or show columns, Export address records, Duplicate address records, Copy address details, and Send messages to selected records.</span></li><li data-list=\"ordered\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">The system uses company address information to maintain accurate company location details and support organizational management across the application.</span></li></ol><p><br></p>",
